Description: DarkHorse, a ZebraLight clone UI for FSM.
    Almost identical to ZL's UI from 2016, but makes sub-sub-level
    configuration easier -- "click, release, hold" instead of
    "6+ double-clicks".
Authors: ToyKeeper
MCU: attiny45, attiny85
Button-Type: momentary
Memory: none, sub-levels, sub-sub-levels
Modes: battcheck, tactical strobe, beacon
Extras: thermal regulation, LVP, dual PWM, triple PWM
